Description: MCP server for LinkedIn profile, company, and job scraping
 linkedin-mcp-server provides a Model Context Protocol (MCP) server
 that enables AI assistants such as Claude to scrape LinkedIn profiles,
 company pages, and job listings using an automated Chromium browser session.
 .
 Supported features:
  - Person profile scraping with configurable section selection
  - Company profile and employee listing extraction
  - Job search and detailed job listing retrieval
  - LinkedIn feed access
  - Secure credential storage with persistent browser session
 .
 The server exposes tools via the MCP protocol and can be integrated with
 any MCP-compatible AI client.
